videos.description: Cameron Hunter lifts the Bison with a 3-pointer to a four-point lead over Arizona.
videos.headline: NDSU's Hunter hits 3 falling down

videos.description: Allonzo Trier drills a step-back 3-pointer with a defender in his face to give the Wildcats the lead.
videos.headline: Arizona's Trier launches step-back 3

videos.description: Allonzo Trier finds Deandre Ayton off the pick and roll at the rim as he finishes with a one-handed alley-oop for Arizona.
videos.headline: Ayton ends the half with a one-handed oop

videos.description: Parker Jackson-Cartwright sends a long pass high for Rawle Alkins along the baseline who slams it home.
videos.headline: Alkins jams for another Arizona alley-oop

videos.description: Arizona's Allonzo Trier goes down hard after banging his left knee on Paul Miller's leg and has to be helped to the locker room.
videos.headline: Trier helped to locker room after banging knee
